\/category\/electric-vehicles\/"},{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org\/","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com#main-nav","name":"ADVICE","url":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/category\/advice\/"},{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org\/","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com#main-nav","name":"FEATURES","url":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/category\/features\/"},{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org\/","@type":"SiteNavigationElement","@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com#main-nav","name":"VIDEOS","url":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/videos\/"}]],"isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com#website"}},{"@type":"NewsArticle","@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/mahindra-xuv700-prices-cut-down-by-up-to-rs-75000\/#newsarticle","url":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/mahindra-xuv700-prices-cut-down-by-up-to-rs-75000\/","headline":"Mahindra XUV700 prices cut down by up to Rs 75,000!","mainEntityOfPage":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/mahindra-xuv700-prices-cut-down-by-up-to-rs-75000\/#webpage","datePublished":"2025-03-25T17:04:13+05:30","dateModified":"2025-03-25T17:04:13+05:30","description":"Mahindra XUV700 prices have been cut down by up to Rs 75,000 depending on the variant. It is the highest price cut for the SUV since launch.","articleSection":"News","articleBody":"Key highlights     \tMahindra XUV700 undergoes a massive price cut   \tAX7 L variants available at Rs 75,000 less   \tHighest ever price cut down for the SUV since launch    Mahindra has cut down the pricing for the top variants of the XUV700. The massive price cut stands up to Rs 75,000, depending on the variant. Check out the complete details of the price cut below.    Also read: New-gen Jeep Compass spied testing, looks like baby Grand Cherokee!  Mahindra XUV700 price slash details  As per the latest price revision, the AX7 and AX7 L trims of the XUV700 have witnessed a price slash. The AX7 variants now cost Rs 45,000 less for the automatic gearbox with a petrol or diesel engine option.    Meanwhile, the AX7 L automatic variants for both petrol and diesel are now cheaper by Rs 75,000. However, the prices for the AX7 manual options, for both petrol and diesel, are unchanged.    With the newly revised prices, the AX7 range now starts from Rs 20.99 lakh for the Petrol AT and goes up to Rs 24.99 lakh for the Diesel AT AWD.    Mind you, this is the biggest price cut for the XUV700 since the SUV was introduced. Initially, the XUV700 was ultra popular but with the launch of Scorpio N, it lost the charm among buyers.    Moreover, the AX7 and AX7 L variants were the only ones equipped with the range-topping features like ADAS. However, the long waiting period and hefty price tag restricted buyers from choosing them.    Now, to balance the demand and supply, Mahindra has cut down the prices only for these top-end trims. Meanwhile, the value-for-money variants like the AX5 Select are still available without any discount or price cut.    Also read: Tata Group to partner with Tesla to supply EV parts internationally  Our verdict  The XUV700 is a refined Mahindra product that offers a comfortable ride quality, powerful engine options, and a solid build quality. However, the segment-first features were only limited to the top variants, which Mahindra has made more affordable than ever now with the price slash.","keywords":["Mahindra"," Mahindra XUV700"," "],"name":"Mahindra XUV700 prices cut down by up to Rs 75,000!","thumbnailUrl":"https:\/\/park.shifting-gears.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/XUV700-Deep-Forest-150x150.jpg","wordCount":"331","timeRequired":"PT1M28S","mainEntity":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/mahindra-xuv700-prices-cut-down-by-up-to-rs-75000\/"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"News Desk","url":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/author\/news-desk\/","sameAs":["http:\/\/www.Shifting-Gears.com"],"image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/0d2496201283abd99a59adc3b16bb2e2?s=96&d=mm&r=g","height":96,"width":96}},"editor":{"@type":"Person","name":"News Desk","url":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/author\/news-desk\/","sameAs":["http:\/\/www.Shifting-Gears.com"],"image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/0d2496201283abd99a59adc3b16bb2e2?s=96&d=mm&r=g","height":96,"width":96}},"publisher":{"@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com#Organization"},"speakable":{"@type":"SpeakableSpecification","xpath":["\/html\/head\/title","\/html\/head\/meta[@name='description']\/@content"]},"image":[{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/mahindra-xuv700-prices-cut-down-by-up-to-rs-75000\/#primaryimage","url":"https:\/\/park.shifting-gears.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/XUV700-Deep-Forest.jpg","width":"1200","height":"675","caption":"Mahindra XUV700"}],"isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/shifting-gears.com\/mahindra-xuv700-prices-cut-down-by-up-to-rs-75000\/#webpage"}}]}]
